{
  "texts": [
    "More objective assessment of the subjectivity is not possible due to the lack of the inter-annotator agreement scores [15].",
    "The data is extracted from both mainstream and alternative media sources, collected through news aggregators (e.g.",
    "Google News, Europe Media Monitor) and fact-checking organisations (e.g.",
    "MediaBiasFactCheck, NewsGuard), respectively.",
    "All of the news articles were published between 2020 to mid 2022."
  ]
}